<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4556752>
    dc:description "FIG 3. Map showing localities of Seticotasteromimus jarawa, 1. – type locality on South Andaman Island, 2. – new records from Malaysia, Sabah, Kinabalu (2700 km away), 3. – Seticotasteromimus brunomanseri sp. nov. Malaysia, Tawau, 4. – Obhylius arboricola gen nov. and sp. nov. Malaysia, Sabah, Kinabalu (base layer: https://www.simplemappr.net)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4556752/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

